News.Title: Agarwal Toughened Glass: Strong Market Debut with 25% Premium
News.Summary: Agarwal Toughened Glass listed on NSE SME at ₹135 per share, a 25% premium to its IPO price of ₹108. The stock further rose to ₹138, 28% above the IPO price. The ₹62.64 crore IPO was oversubscribed 9.89 times, with strong interest from non-institutional buyers and retail investors.
